A teenager has been arrested after a 15-year-old girl was allegedly raped. Teenage boy, 16, arrested after alleged rape of girl, 15, in Cumbernauld A teenager has been arrested after a 15-year-old girl was allegedly raped.The 16-year-old boy is being held in connection with the serious sexual assault in Beechwood Road in Cumbernauld, North Lanarkshire, on October 11, police said.A report will be sent to the procurator fiscal.It is expected he will appear at Airdrie Sheriff Court tomorrow. 